Odaily Planet Daily News According to Spot On Chain monitoring, many whales hoarded WIF and PEPE from Binance today: 
1. Whale "0xf37" withdrew 375.35 billion PEPE (US$3.73 million) 3 hours ago, which was the first time to open a position; 
2. Whale "A3kTT" returned after 2 years of dormancy and withdrew 6.5 million WIF (US$5.19 million) 9 hours ago; 
3. Whale "4x3M8" withdrew 9 million WIF (US$7.42 million) 11 hours ago, and it is said that it lost US$1.35 million (-8.74%) in its first WIF transaction.
